STATE EX REL. EVANS
v.
CLERK OF SCIOTO CTY. COMMON PLEAS COURT, PROBATE DIV. 2017-1724 Supreme Court of Ohio. March 8, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

In Mandamus. On respondent's motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed. O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell, Kennedy, Fischer, and DeWine, JJ., concur. French, J., would dismiss the cause as moot.

DeGenaro, J., not participating.
